author: kkrouse
msg: XMLBEANS-104: Tables descriptors are created for simple user defined types (a type based on one of the build-in 20)
This patch solves the first half of this issue. Column datatypes are correctly
set for elements and attributes that use the user defined type who's primitive
type is one of the built in types. Table descriptor are still being created
